description: PDX Bus Tracker tells you arrivals for all buses for a given Stop ID. Invoke by calling Open PDX Bus Tracker, provide the Stop ID and it will respond with all Buses, Scheduled times and Next arrival times. Disclaimer; the app may not be suitable for all ages.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Launch P. D. X. Bus Tracker.
Alexa, Ask P. D. X. Bus Tracker for two two six six.
Alexa, Ask P. D. X. Bus Tracker for help
name: PDX Bus Tracker
shortDescription: PDX Bus Tracker. Next Bus Arrivals for various Stop IDs in PDX
